data.description: NO POWER BILLS AS LONG AS YOU DON'T USE OVER THE KW THAT IS ALLOWED WITH THE SOLAR PANELS ! Enjoy this 3/2 home that is just under 1 year old! This home is conveniently located to schools,worship,retail and dinning. This home offers an open floor plan that is perfect for entertaining. The living room is open to the kitchen which has a wonderful bar and plenty of cabinets. The master bedroom offers a huge master bathroom and walk in closet. Here you will find Low E energy star rated windows,architechural shingles,soft close cabinets,a tankless water heater and solar panels to help with that summer electric bill.
